A subset of the MiDAS example data

A smaller subset of MiDAS with 50 samples from 2 Danish Wastewater Treatment Plants; Aalborg West and Aalborg East.

data(AalborgWWTPs)

Format

An object of class "ampvis2". See amp_load.

Examples

data(AalborgWWTPs)
